      "module_path": "tddd::fs_lint_config_loader",
      "docs": "Filesystem implementation of LintConfigLoader. Holds a fully-resolved path to the lint config file (either the workspace default .harness/catalogue-lint/config.json or a --rules-file CLI override). CLI composition resolves which path to use before constructing FsLintConfigLoader::new(path). load() reads from self.path with no additional argument. Fail-closed: returns LintConfigLoaderError::MissingFile if the file does not exist — no silent fallback to default rules (per OS-10).",
